lor)|Violet]] \n* [[Alpha Omega Alpha Honor Medical Society]], \u0391\u03a9\u0391 ([[medical students, physicians]]), {{color box|#228B22}} [[Shades of green#Forest green|Forest Green]], {{color box|#FFCC00}} [[Gold (color)|Gold]] and {{color box|#FFFFFF}} [[White]]\n* Iota Tau Alpha, \u0399\u03a4\u0391 ([[Athletic Training]])<ref>{{cite web|last1=Mankin|first1=Carlie|last2=Doherty-Restrepo|first2=Jennifer|title=Iota Tau Alpha: The Athletic Training Honor Society|url=http://www.nata.org/blog/todd-christman/iota-tau-alpha-athletic-training-honor-society|publisher=National Athletic Trainers' Association's Blog|language=en|date=April 8, 2016|access-date=2017-02-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170211155947/http://www.nata.org/blog/todd-christman/iota-tau-alpha-athletic-training-honor-society|archive-date=2017-02-11|url-status=live}}</ref>\n* [[Nu Rho Psi]], \u039d\u03a1\u03a8 ([[Neuroscience]])\n* [[Rho Chi]], \u03a1\u03a7 ([[pharmacy]]), colors: {{color box|#7851A9}} [[Royal Purple|Purple]] and {{color box|#FFFFFF}} [[White]]\n* [[Sigma Theta Tau]], \u03a3\u0398\u03a4 ([[nursing]]), colors: {{color box|#9932CC}} [[Orchid (color)#Dark orchid|Orchid]] and {{color box|#FFFFFF}} [[White]]\n* Sigma Phi Alpha, \u03a3\u03a6\u0391 ([[Oral hygiene|dental hygiene]])<ref>[http://sigma-phi-alpha.org/ Sigma Phi Alpha website] {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140521032636/http://sigma-phi-alpha.org/ |date=2014-05-21 }}, accessed 20 May 2014</ref>\n* [[Upsilon Phi Delta]], \u03a5\u03a6\u0394 ([[health administration]])\n\n=====Agriculture=====\n<!--Editors: to add color swatches, see the Talk page for instructions.-->\n*[[Gamma Sigma Delta]], \u0393\u03a3\u0394, (Honor Society of [[Agriculture]])<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.gammasigmadelta.org/|title=Gamma Sigma Delta \u2013 The Honor Society of Agriculture|website=www.gammasigmadelta.org|access-date=2014-02-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140224112352/http://www.gammasigmadelta.org/|archive-