180927074613/http://etasigmagamma.org/ |date=2018-09-27 }}, accessed 24 June 2014</ref>\n\n=====Leadership=====\n<!--Editors: to add color swatches, see the Talk page for instructions.-->\n* Order of The Key Honor Society<ref>{{cite web|title=Home - Order of the Key|url=http://www.orderofthekey.org/|access-date=2012-01-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120205043523/http://www.orderofthekey.org/|archive-date=2012-02-05|url-status=live}}</ref> ([[leadership]])\n*[[Mortar Board]] (leadership), colors: {{color box|#FFD700}} [[Gold (color)|Gold]] and {{color box|#C0C0C0}} [[Silver (color)|Silver]] \n*[[National Residence Hall Honorary]], NRHH ([[Dormitory|Residence hall]] leadership/service)\n*[[Omicron Delta Kappa]], \u039f\u0394\u039a (leadership and academic; juniors, seniors, graduate students, alumni, faculty and staff, honorary)\n*[[Sigma Alpha Lambda]], \u03a3\u0391\u039b ([[leadership]])\n*[[Sigma Alpha Pi]], \u03a3\u0391\u03a0 (leadership)\n*[[Phi Kappa Alpha]], \u03a6\u039a\u0391 (leadership)\n\n=====Military=====\n<!--Editors: to add color swatches, see the Talk page for instructions.-->\n*[[Arnold Air Society]], ([[United States Air Force]] [[cadet]]s)\n*[[Pershing Rifles]] ([[United States armed forces]])\n*[[Scabbard and Blade]] ([[Reserve Officers' Training Corps|ROTC]] [[cadet]]s and [[Midshipman|midshipmen]])\n\n=====Other=====\n<!--Editors: to add color swatches, see the Talk page for instructions.-->\nAlpha Mu, AM, (Agricultural Systems Management)\n*[[Beta Phi Mu]], \u0392\u03a6\u039c ([[library science]]/[[information science]]/[[information technology]])\n*[[Chi Epsilon Pi]], \u03a7\u0395\u03a0 ([[meteorology]])\n*[[Chi Sigma Iota]], \u03a7\u03a3\u0399 ([[counseling]])\n*[[Epsilon Pi Tau]], \u0395\u03a0\u03a4 ([[technology]])\n*[[Epsilon Tau Pi]], \u0395\u03a4\u03a0 ([[Eagle Scout (Boy Scouts of America)|Eagle Scouts]])\n*[[Gamma Nu Eta]], \u0393\u039d\u0397 (information technology)\n*[[Nu Rho Psi]], \u039d\u03a1\u03a8 ([[neuroscience]])\