 Honor Society]] ([[high school]] general)\n*[[National Honorary Beta Club]] ([[high school]] general)\n*[[National Honorary Junior Beta Club]] ([[middle school]] general)\n*[[National Junior Honor Society]] ([[middle school]] general)\n*[[Quill and Scroll]] (journalism)\n*[[Science National Honor Society]] (science)\n*[[Soci\u00e9t\u00e9 Honoraire de Fran\u00e7ais]] ([[French language|French]])\n*[[Spanish National Honor Society]] (''Sociedad Honoraria Hisp\u00e1nica'') ([[Spanish language|Spanish]])\n*[[Technology Student Association]] (STEM), colors: {{color box|red}} [[Red]] {{color box|blue}} [[blue]] {{color box|white}} [[White]] \n*[[Tri-M|Tri-M Music Honor Society]] ([[music]]), colors: {{color box|pink}} [[Pink]]\n\n=== Vocational, technical, and workforce education ===\n<!--Editors: to add color swatches, see the Talk page for instructions.-->\n* [[National Technical Honor Society]]\n\n===Two-year colleges and community colleges===\n<!--Editors: to add color swatches, see the Talk page for instructions.-->\n*[[Alpha Beta Gamma]], \u0391\u0392\u0393 ([[business]] at [[two-year college]]s)\n*[[Alpha Gamma Sigma (honor society)|Alpha Gamma Sigma]], \u0391\u0393\u03a3  ([[California Community Colleges System|California community colleges]])\n*[[Phi Theta Kappa]], \u03a6\u0398\u039a (All academic fields at [[Community college|community]] and [[junior college]]s)\n*[[Psi Beta]], \u03a8\u0392 ([[psychology]] at [[two-year college]]s)\n*[[Sigma Kappa Delta]], \u03a3\u039a\u0394 ([[English studies|English]] at [[Community college|community]] and [[junior college]]s)\n*[[Sigma Zeta]], \u03a3\u0396 ([[natural sciences]]/[[mathematics]]/[[computer science]] - Associate membership available for [[Community college|community]] and [[junior college]]s)\n*[[Beta Chi]] \u0392\u03a7 ([[criminal justice]] at [[two-year college]]s)\n\n==Boy Scouts==\n<!--Editors: to add color swatches, see the Talk page for instructions.-->\n*[[Order of the Arrow]], National BSA Honor Society